and whatnot on these cases and change the bandage

10:29.620 --> 10:48.692
and all for these foot rot cases, you know. after 
self-pyridine was available, you take two ounces

10:49.533 --> 11:00.008
of that and put it in a pint of water and give it 
intravenously to the animal and turn him loose.

11:00.449 --> 11:01.430
Not ever bandage him. And this old lady wasn't 
going to pay me because she came out to treat that

11:01.750 --> 11:08.480
cow and didn't even put a bandage on her foot. I 
said, well, the cow got all right, didn't it? Yeah,

11:10.803 --> 11:12.646
