hard enough. That's right. They haven't worked

11:27.102 --> 11:29.530
hard enough. Another thing that's come about in 
these modern years is the discovery of what causes

11:30.218 --> 11:38.910
wheat pasture poisoning. That used to be a big 
problem to us. Those old cows, you'd push them

11:42.635 --> 11:49.604
around and they'd become paralyzed and fight you 
and all that. And of course, it's magnesium

11:49.704 --> 11:52.347
deficiency. We've...

