40:05.150 --> 40:07.214
individuals. And we all hung together like just a 
bunch of peas in a pod, and whenever things weren't

40:07.234 --> 40:13.885
going right or we had a problem or we didn't think we 
were doing client right. We'd all get together and

40:17.692 --> 40:21.058
see what was wrong and try to straighten the thing 
out. That's the way it ought to be. But the new

40:22.201 --> 40:32.161
group, they'll come if you're going to have a 
special technique, new technique on fracture

40:22.201 --> 40:32.161
fixation or something like that. They'll get them 
out, but if it's just to talk over how we can better

40:36.477 --> 40:40.741
serve the community and so forth. Okay, I'm ready. 
