41:33.920 --> 41:41.547
take my family first, not this family, but my 
brothers and sisters. I

41:41.687 --> 42:02.087
was very fortunate to be a member of a family such

41:41.687 --> 42:02.087
as I had.

42:03.367 --> 42:08.476
Not an ounce of jealousy nor greed in any one of 
them. Who were your brothers and sisters? Well,

42:12.282 --> 42:15.909
W.L. William Anderson. Who was named after your 
